commitResults.messageTitle: Add storage feature, more exceptions for bad storage
commitResults.messageBody:
Yap does not have a storage feature, resulting in all data being loss when program is stopped

Storage feature is necessary as users will want tasks to be saved even when they exit the program

Create such storage feature which saves the task as Task Type | Completion Status | Duration related stuff
